{"tid":1066497,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人check過婚姻記錄","createTime":"2019-03-18T02:39:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T08:35:16.000Z","uid":180913,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d3605ec5fc677f063f4a97c2d21b8ecca2217cbc","tid":1066497,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:39:07.000Z","msg":"屋企老人家臨老入花叢（都係老野遇上大陸西case), 收埋十幾年而加入醫院即刻出黎搶身家。<br />\n屋企人問阿爺有冇同個大陸女人結婚，女人話有，但阿爺話冇各執一詞。<br />\n我打左電話去婚姻註冊處，個職員勁唔熟仲係度搵notes話知道日期先做到，我問話有哂男方身份證正本再加女方身份證資料做唔做到？<br />\n佢就改口咩都話可能可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我無呢方面知道上網google話出律師信就有得check?<br />\n<br />\n而加屋企人煩緊公司律師個邊，叫我暗底去check 阿爺有冇同個女人結婚。<br />\n我想問有冇咩渠道可以知道佢有冇結婚，而加就係唔知有冇結婚點嘔個日期出查？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba9a427bab22543880048bcd251ee6349d982d6","tid":1066497,"uid":193192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/bdmreg/applybdm.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fresidents%2Fimmigration%2Fbdmreg%2Fapplybdm.htm&d=0ENX7tHwQhT09cvOu3%2F4M7500bRp0Z5eW4%2BYbKsxGJA%3D&h=6a47acc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigration/bdmreg/applybdm.htm</a>"},{"pid":"13142059ffeaf28b88d54b991b98c26f25cca9d0","tid":1066497,"uid":180913,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8ba9a427bab22543880048bcd251ee6349d982d6","tid":1066497,"uid":193192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T02:41:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gov.hk/tc/residents/immigrat